@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Doormats for everyone";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center" style="color: #D32F2F;">Welcome to <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Doormats.com</span></h1>

    <div class="mt-4" style="max-width: 800px; margin: auto;">
        <p>
            Ever thought about what lies beneath those <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #D32F2F;">dusty shoes</span>,
            vibrant heels, or rugged boots? Well, it's us! The unsung heroes of your entryway,
            the humble guardians of clean floors, and the first line of defense against muddy invaders – the
            <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #D32F2F;">mighty Doormats</span>!
        </p>

        <p>
            Here at <span style="color: #D32F2F;">Doormats.com</span>, we firmly believe in giving you a <span style="color: #388E3C;">grand entrance</span>,
            every single time. Because why? We're way more than just pieces of fabric you step on. We're mood-setters,
            <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #388E3C;">style-makers</span>, and sometimes, even a witty joke-teller to tickle your guests' feet (and funny bones!).
        </p>

        <p>
            Did you know a doormat's life isn't all that... flat? We face rain, shine, snow, and the occasional cat nap.
            Yet, we're resilient, stylish, and always up for a good foot rub. If we had a motto, it'd be,
            "<span style="color: #D32F2F;">Wipe your shoes, but never your smiles!</span>"
        </p>

        <p>
            So, whether you're here to find the perfect mat that says, "<span style="color: #388E3C;">Home Sweet Home</span>,"
            or that cheeky one that goes, "You again?", <span style="color: #D32F2F;">Doormats.com</span>
            is the one-stop-shop for all your underfoot needs. Dive in and discover a world where every step, slip, and shuffle is celebrated!
        </p>

        <p>Remember, life might get dirty, but your floors don't have to. Choose a doormat that speaks your language. After all, first impressions start at the doorstep!</p>
    </div>
</div>
